$ Software quality assurance

Goals:
  • Increase customer satisfaction
  • Ensure conformance to requirements and standards
  • Reduce life cycle costs, especially maintenance

Tasks
  • Defect prevention
  • Defect detection
  • Defect removal

{ Quality Management System (QMS)

  QMS is a collection of business processes focused on consistently meeting customer requirements and enhancing their satisfaction

}

